<HEADLINE>
<P>
LACC SCHEDULES MEMORIAL FOR DR. JOHN LOMBARDI 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A memorial service for Dr. John Lombardi, president of Los Angeles City College 
from 1955 to 1966, will be held Tuesday at 1:30 p.m. in the campus Student 
Center. 
</P>
<P>
Lombardi was 85 when he died Feb. 28 in Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
After retiring from City College in 1966 he became assistant superintendent of 
all the community colleges for the Los Angeles district. 
</P>
</TEXT>
