than 300 pounds by the end of spring practice. ; Photo, Tackle Joe Heinz has 
lost nearly 90 pounds in four months. ; Photo, Senior Chuck Hardaway has 
trimmed off about 35 pounds. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
