Matadors (5-9, 3-4) at Bolsa Grande. 
</P>
<P>
Garden Grove 9, Santiago 0 -- Stephanie Smith (12-7) pitched a no-hitter, 
striking out 12, for the Argonauts (14-8, 6-1) at Garden Grove. Kim Clark had 
two hits and four RBIs for Garden Grove. 
</P>
<P>
In the Olympic League: 
</P>
<P>
