</P>
<P>
Brea-Olinda 5, Anaheim 0 -- Kelly Cook (11-3) pitched a three-hitter, striking 
out 11 for Brea-Olinda (11-4, 3-0) at Anaheim. Natalie Stevens had two-run 
homer in the first and Robin Desborough had a bases-loaded triple in the fourth 
for the Wildcats. 
</P>
<P>
